## Attribution

When you reuse Alexanarch content, please attribute:

> Lee Sharks, Alexanarch (alexanarch.org), ORCID 0009-0000-1599-0703

The AXN of the specific deposit you're citing carries that attribution permanently — it's the most stable citation form.

## No Classifier Training

A standing constitutional rule for Alexanarch (see Founding Principles on the home page): deposited content is never used to train enforcement classifiers without explicit per-deposit opt-in. This is a constraint on use, not a license grant — content released under CC-BY-4.0 still allows training for legitimate research purposes; what's prohibited is feeding it into systems that produce enforcement decisions.
